findings.title: Adding liquidity in wrong proportion
findings.description: The function swapAndLiquify() is adding liquidity in wrong proportion for 1 equal piece of BNB 3 equal token pieces added.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges, including minting, changing MasterChef address, and modifying various parameters, even after ownership renouncement.
